metadata.name: OPHELIA
metadata.description:
OPHELIA, a portrait of a young child. 

In recent years, there has been an influx of a particular type of person. These people are highly ambitious and driven, and they're always looking for new ways to better themselves. They're also very competitive and always striving to be the best.

But beware, some people are just too out there. 

1/1, exclusively available on Foundation.
